/target
**/*.rs.bk
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store

# Claude Code per-machine state
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/launch.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Node / Wrangler
**/node_modules/
**/.wrangler/

# Secrets — belt-and-suspenders. Real secrets live in ~/.hellodb/env.sh
# (outside the repo) and Cloudflare Worker secrets (never on disk).
# These patterns exist so an accidental local file drop doesn't make it
# into a commit. Matches `.env`, `.env.local`, `.dev.vars` (wrangler),
# `*.secret`, `*.secrets`, `credentials*.json`, any `.pem` / `.key` file
# outside target/ (identity.key lives in ~/.hellodb, never the repo).
.env
.env.*
.dev.vars
*.secret
*.secrets
credentials*.json
*.pem
*.key
!identity.key.sample

# Platform-specific binaries (bundled on demand by make bundle / CI)
/plugin/bin/hellodb
/plugin/bin/hellodb-mcp
/plugin/bin/hellodb-brain
